\subsection{Method \code{get_spot_accounts()}}{
Get Spot Account List

Retrieves all spot accounts for the authenticated user, optionally filtered
by currency or account type. Each row represents a single account with its
current balance, available funds, and holds.
\subsection{Workflow}{
\enumerate{
\item \strong{Request}: Authenticated GET with optional query filters.
\item \strong{Parsing}: Row-binds the list of account objects into a \code{data.table}.
Returns an empty \code{data.table} if no accounts match the filter.
}
}

\subsection{API Endpoint}{

\verb{GET https://api.kucoin.com/api/v1/accounts}
}

\subsection{Official Documentation}{

\href{https://www.kucoin.com/docs-new/rest/account-info/account-funding/get-account-list-spot}{KuCoin Get Spot Account List}

